{"id":423,"ayahs":[{"number":36,"arabic":"وَمَا كَانَ لِمُؤْمِنٍۢ وَلَا مُؤْمِنَةٍ إِذَا قَضَى ٱللَّهُ وَرَسُولُهُۥٓ أَمْرًا أَن يَكُونَ لَهُمُ ٱلْخِيَرَةُ مِنْ أَمْرِهِمْ ۗ وَمَن يَعْصِ ٱللَّهَ وَرَسُولَهُۥ فَقَدْ ضَلَّ ضَلَٰلًۭا مُّبِينًۭا","translation":"Now whenever God and His Apostle have decided a matter, it is not for a believing man or a believing woman to claim freedom of choice insofar as they themselves are concerned: for he who [thus] rebels against God and His Apostle has already, most obviously, gone astray.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/3569.mp3","surahId":33,"words":[{"id":38449,"position":1,"arabic":"وَمَا","translation":"এবং নেই","audioUrl":"wbw/033_036_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38450,"position":2,"arabic":"كَانَ","translation":"অধিকার","audioUrl":"wbw/033_036_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38451,"position":3,"arabic":"لِمُؤْمِنٍۢ","translation":"কোন মু'মিন পুরুষের জন্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_036_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38452,"position":4,"arabic":"وَلَا","translation":"আর না","audioUrl":"wbw/033_036_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38453,"position":5,"arabic":"مُؤْمِنَةٍ","translation":"মু'মিন নারীর (জন্যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/033_036_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38454,"position":6,"arabic":"إِذَا","translation":"যখন","audioUrl":"wbw/033_036_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38455,"position":7,"arabic":"قَضَى","translation":"সিদ্ধান্ত দেন","audioUrl":"wbw/033_036_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38456,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱللَّهُ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/033_036_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38457,"position":9,"arabic":"وَرَسُولُهُۥٓ","translation":"ও রাসূল তাঁর","audioUrl":"wbw/033_036_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38458,"position":10,"arabic":"أَمْرًا","translation":"কোনো বিষয়ের","audioUrl":"wbw/033_036_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":38459,"position":11,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/033_036_011.mp3",